## Deployment & Configuration

### GitHub Repository Setup

**Repository Structure:**
```
ramy-eid-portfolio/
├── reports/
│   └── 08_final_delivery/
│       ├── index.html
│       ├── css/
│       │   ├── main.css
│       │   └── dark-mode.css
│       ├── assets/
│       └── _redirects
├── .gitignore
├── README.md
├── netlify.toml
└── reports/
```

**Git Configuration:**
- Branch management for features
- Commit history with descriptive messages
- Proper .gitignore setup
- README documentation

### Netlify Deployment

**Configuration Files:**

**netlify.toml:**
```toml
[build]
  publish = "reports/08_final_delivery"
[build.environment]
  NODE_VERSION = "18"
[[redirects]]
  from = "/*"
  to = "/index.html"
  status = 200
[[headers]]
  for = "/*"
  [headers.values]
    X-Frame-Options = "DENY"
    X-XSS-Protection = "1; mode=block"
    X-Content-Type-Options = "nosniff"
    Referrer-Policy = "strict-origin-when-cross-origin"
    Content-Security-Policy = "default-src 'self'; script-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline'; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' https://fonts.googleapis.com; font-src 'self' https://fonts.gstatic.com; img-src 'self' data: https:; connect-src 'self';"
```

**_redirects:**
```
/*    /index.html   200
/projects    /projects.html   200
/experience  /experience.html 200
/about       /about.html      200
/contact     /contact.html    200
```

**Security Headers:**
- X-Frame-Options: DENY
- X-XSS-Protection: 1; mode=block
- X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
- Content-Security-Policy
- Referrer-Policy

